# ClawBio environment variables
# Copy to .env and fill in your keys

# FLock API — open-source model inference for intelligent routing
# Sign up at https://platform.flock.io
# Required for: Bio Orchestrator LLM routing (--provider flock)
# Not required for: all other skills (they are pure Python, no LLM needed)
FLOCK_API_KEY=your-flock-api-key-here
